object.text: Fun atmosphere ... delicious food ~ super sweet young lady as our waitress.  :)

venue.name: Red Robin Gourmet Burgers and Brews

object.text: Guacamole bacon burger and bottomless sides ftw!
You can choose your own meat for your burger, Angus beef, chicken, bison, garden. Choose your cheese. Choose buns or a lettuce wrap. Choose your burger! Not sure there is a “wrong” burger here!!

potato salad's incredible! brisket's very good. +1

object.text: Easily the best establishment we've checked out since we moved. Try the wings! The crust is killer, specialty pies on point, and beer selection is solid.

object.text: Great experience. Food was done as expected. Even the special order items (gluten sensitivity) came out perfect. The staff was attentive, and our server John was amazing!
